text: Ülo Tulik (11 May 1957 – 30 April 2022) was a Estonian agronomist and politician. Tulik was born in Meremäe, Estonia. He was the Võru County Governor from 2005 until 2010. He was Mayor of Võru from 2010 until 2011.ur Tulik died on 30 April 2022 in Võru at the age of 64. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Estonian scientists Category:Estonian mayors Category:Agricultural engineers
